channel.title: Magic Interface Return?
channel.description:
Quick question...
Just wondering if it was possible to make it so it *Returns* to the magic interface after High Alching or Low Alching?
[i]---Please, I repeat please, Do not tell me just to put (setSidebarInterface 6,11blahblah); under High alch and Low Alch... All that means is it changes your magic tab to regular magic.
Thank you, Mod Adam
